<br>
Sunderfury<br>
LORE ITEM MAGIC ITEM NO DROP  <br>
Damage: 25<br>
Delay: 36 <br>
Weight: 7.5 <br>
Weapon Skill: Two Hand Slash <br>
Classes: Warrior  <br>
Races: All Races  <br>
Inventory Slot: Primary Melee<br>
Planar Item: Yes <br>
Effect: Haste <br>
Type: Permanent <br>
Rarity: Very Rare  <br>
Level to Attain: 46  <br>
<br>
It says that the haste is 36% Permanent. I am not a very Uber Warrior, I use SCHW as a hatste item till I hopefully can afford something else.<br>
<br>
In a secondary tank position, this looks like a fine weapon. You get the DMG bonus of the slower weapon, but the damage of something nearly 25/25. This is before hooking up with a chanter or a bard. <br>
<br>
What are the thoughts on this weapon, Besides the fact that it looks like I mugged Gix on the way to the raid.<br>
<br>
Narcon<br>
56 WAR <br>
Torv<br>
 <br>
